How to use (for all versions):
- Make sure you have an instance of mongodb running
- npm install -d
- node app.js
- Point your browser to http://localhost:3000
- You will be asked to login with a Google Apps account with a @thesentinelproject.org google apps email

Version 2.0
- URL https://github.com/thesentinelproject/threatwiki_node/tree/v2.0
- Specify the NODE_ENV to Production because the development environment is currently not supported: 
	ie: export NODE_ENV=production

Tests
The tests are only testing the REST API
To run the tests, go to the api folder
Type: node api_tests.js